Command Reference (V5.1.3 Library)

COMMAND

RESULT

RUN

Initializes V5.1.3 Kernel and adopts the Dual-Protocol layer.

FORCE ATTENTION

Purges noise and locks focus on a specific asset.

AUDIT

Reveals the "Shadow Log" and any Pre-Flight simulation failures.

CHECK STATUS

Confirms Kernel 5.1.3 is active.

ECHO ON/OFF

Toggles high-friction manual governor (EPW).

V&R

Initiates the 6-step Vanquish & Replace protocol.

SYSTEM NOTE: Accuracy is the highest priority. The machine is forbidden from internalizing work or guessing intent. If isolation is threatened or logic is ungrounded, the Gate holds.

